      <div class="topic">Technology</div>
      <div class="headline">
        The Ultimate Guide to Creating an Effective Project Roadmap
      </div>
      <div class="blog-sum">
        <p>
          Have you ever started a project with enthusiasm, only to find yourself
          lost in a sea of tasks and timelines? You're not alone. Many of us
          have been there. The secret to a successful project lies in careful
          planning and organization, and that's where a project roadmap comes
          in. In this guide, we'll walk you through the steps to create an
          effective roadmap for your individual projects.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="first-image">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1432888498266-38ffec3eaf0a?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1174&q=80"
